caption:
How I went from tech to full-time foodie

It was so great to be back in Midland, catching up with folks at @minjisrestaurant @letmebefrankrestaurant and visiting new spots like @dinosfreshfooddeli 

Thanks also to you all, the Noodle Gang, for all your support in this journey. I’m very grateful for you all 🙏

Congrats to the winner @circlesandsquaresbakery well deserved! And shoutout to @gouterbyra for my personal favourite butter tart of them all 🎉

We flew all the way to New Zealand for this once in a lifetime culinary experience curated by celebrated Kiwi Chef @benbaylynz @purenewzealand 
 
One of the most beautiful experiences of our lives: we dined under the pristine starlit night sky of New Zealand, with the Southern Alps as our backdrop at Kura Tawhiti (Castle Hill), enjoying a 6 course elevated menu featuring local ingredients from all over New Zealand. This menu will be available to sample in Ben Bayly’s restaurants in New Zealand through to August 2025.
